{"tid":196613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超級月亮不夠看！「粉紅月亮」今晚現身日本","createTime":"2017-04-11T12:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:53:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b926e249f970af3e68da75a63c05e80c981adb0","tid":196613,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpQmzfCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpQmzfCK.jpg&h=8e699666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本每年在櫻花盛開、又適逢滿月的時節，夜空中的月亮就可能會呈現粉紅色。（圖擷自推特）</span><br />\n2017-04-11  18:23<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕很多人對月亮的印象就是會發出白色的光，然而日本卻會出現粉紅色的月亮，而今年會出現粉紅月亮的日期就是今天（4/11）。<br />\n綜合報導指出，日本每年在櫻花盛開、又適逢滿月的時節，夜空中的月亮就會呈現粉紅色。每當天空出現粉紅月亮，很多人都會搶著拍照。而今年粉紅月亮出現的時間是在4月11日。很多人喜歡將月亮也和愛情連結在一起，據傳粉紅色月亮降臨的那天，人的戀愛運就會一直上升，因此是個適合表白的時機。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/apr/11/images/bigPic/400_400/phpbKSGtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fapr%2F11%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpbKSGtQ.jpg&h=e2fd16f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">據傳粉紅色月亮降臨的那天，戀愛運會一直上升，因此是個適合表白的時機。（圖擷自推特）</span><br />\nh[img]ttp://<a href=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/apr/11/images/bigPic/400_400/phpgwRHZ8.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fapr%2F11%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpgwRHZ8.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi654%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bc54e7c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fapr%2F11%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpgwRHZ8.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&h=3a94f3bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/apr/11/images/bigPic/400_400/phpgwRHZ8.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年的粉紅月亮。（圖擷自推特）</span><br />\n雖然今年的粉紅月亮還沒出現，不過日本推特上已經有很多網友在對此討論，也有不少人貼出往年的粉紅月亮照片。<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/deathbattlefanon/images/6/66/Sailor_Mini_Moon.png/revision/latest?cb=20150514005418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fdeathbattlefanon%2Fimages%2F6%2F66%2FSailor_Mini_Moon.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20150514005418&h=31be2a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2033098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2033098&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi654%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bc8ad96b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2033098&h=fd4d6581\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2033098</a>"},{"pid":"23f13433c71be4749bc895f9ddaa469cb7606d54","tid":196613,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:23:10.000Z","msg":"粉閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b897a5ba632f2c2f8cf33a2692e88a02df94fa","tid":196613,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abb9900ba77c634710d204e4da8ea04d425f4ce","tid":196613,"uid":65887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201508/mobile01-b5e8ef00c7d450b4ef601ebdc54038a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201508%2Fmobile01-b5e8ef00c7d450b4ef601ebdc54038a8.jpg&h=7460393a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac9ef165324e4f517ef24af7fad0f1d6b5c20b0d","tid":196613,"uid":89220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201508/mobile01-b5e8ef00c7d450b4ef601ebdc54038a